ced [æks]. She also drops copula: "He by the area where his daddy fiancée house is." where an 'is' would be included before by in SAE.%0a%3c %0a%3c The article charges that because none of the jurors were African American and presumably weren't AAVE speakers, they could very well misunderstand or judge Rachel's character and by extension her testimony by the way she spoke.%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
